## Design Tokens

### Colors
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| --color-primary | #... | Primary actions, links, brand |
| --color-primary-foreground | #... | Text on primary |
| --color-secondary | #... | Secondary actions, accents |
| --color-secondary-foreground | #... | Text on secondary |
| --color-background | #... | Page background |
| --color-foreground | #... | Primary text |
| --color-muted | #... | Secondary text, captions |
| --color-muted-foreground | #... | Text on muted |
| --color-border | #... | Borders, dividers |
| --color-input | #... | Input backgrounds |
| --color-ring | #... | Focus rings |
| --color-destructive | #... | Delete, error actions |
| --color-destructive-foreground | #... | Text on destructive |
| --color-success | #... | Success indicators |
| --color-warning | #... | Warning indicators |

### Typography Scale
| Token | Size | Line-height | Weight | Usage |
|-------|------|-------------|--------|-------|
| --text-xs | 0.75rem | 1rem | 400 | Captions, labels |
| --text-sm | 0.875rem | 1.25rem | 400 | Body small, help text |
| --text-base | 1rem | 1.5rem | 400 | Body text |
| --text-lg | 1.125rem | 1.75rem | 500 | Subheadings |
| --text-xl | 1.25rem | 1.75rem | 600 | Card titles |
| --text-2xl | 1.5rem | 2rem | 600 | Section headers |
| --text-3xl | 1.875rem | 2.25rem | 700 | Page titles |
| --text-4xl | 2.25rem | 2.5rem | 700 | Hero text |

### Spacing Scale (8px grid)
| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| --space-1 | 0.25rem (4px) | Tight inline |
| --space-2 | 0.5rem (8px) | Inline gap |
| --space-3 | 0.75rem (12px) | Compact padding |
| --space-4 | 1rem (16px) | Standard padding |
| --space-6 | 1.5rem (24px) | Section gap |
| --space-8 | 2rem (32px) | Large gap |
| --space-12 | 3rem (48px) | Section padding |
| --space-16 | 4rem (64px) | Page padding |

### Border Radius
| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| --radius-sm | 0.25rem | Checkboxes, badges |
| --radius-md | 0.375rem | Inputs, buttons |
| --radius-lg | 0.5rem | Cards, modals |
| --radius-xl | 0.75rem | Large containers |
| --radius-full | 9999px | Pills, avatars |

### Shadows
| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| --shadow-sm | 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05) | Subtle elevation |
| --shadow-md | 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1) | Cards, dropdowns |
| --shadow-lg | 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1) | Modals |
| --shadow-xl | 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1) | Top-level overlays |

## Motion

| Property | Value | Usage |
|----------|-------|-------|
| Duration fast | 150ms | Hover, focus, micro |
| Duration normal | 200ms | Transitions, fade |
| Duration slow | 300ms | Page transitions, modals |
| Easing default | cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) | Standard transitions |
| Easing in | cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 1, 1) | Elements entering |
| Easing out | cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1) | Elements exiting |

